        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 75. Phylogenetic tree of specimens of the species related to Anolis boulengerianus from a maximum-likelihood analysis of DNA sequences of two mitochondrial genes: (a) 16S rRNA and (b) CO1. A scale bar is indicated. The numbers at nodes are bootstrap values. The tree is rooted with the species Anolis macrinii. For designation of OTUs see text." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4931113/files/figure.png" .

